cs.CL, cs.SD, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SI

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with automatic speech recognition (ASR) systems and language modeling. It could also belong to cs.SD (Sound) as it deals with audio data. Additionally, it involves machine learning techniques such as neural networks, which could place it in the sub-categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the proposed system aims to improve the accuracy of ASR, which could fall under the sub-category of cs.SI (Signal Processing).
